%h1
  About BikeDeed

- cache('about_counts', expires_in: 24.hours) do
  %p
    Founded by Ken Woodruff in 2018.

%p
BikeDeed is a Decentralized Registry for Bicycles running on the Ethereum Blockchain. Our primary goals are to combat bike theft, validate ownership, and maintain service records. 
A Carfax for Bikes - only better.

%p
Increased government spending on eco-friendly infrastructure and growing enthusiasm for pedal-assist technology is making bicycles a much more important part of people's lives. Blockchain technology infuses a new level of proof, trust and confidence into this burgeoning consumer market.


